categories: Category:Cut content from Star Wars: Empire at War

nodes.text: Hut-tina was Jabba the Hutt's fourth cousin.

Unused information in MasterTextFile.dat in Star Wars: Empire at War: Forces of Corruption indicate that Hut-tina was going to contact Tyber Zann in the Zann Consortium tutorial campaign in order to buy Buzz Droids in a black market on Kashyyyk. However the mission, along with the character, were cut for the final version of the game. The subtitles and the audio for Hut-tina's dialogue still exists in the game's data.
